The paper deals with predicting quality of experience (QoE) for streaming video, which involves machine learning and video quality metrics. This suggests that it could belong to multiple sub-categories, including multimedia (cs.MM), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), and information theory (cs.IT).
